ource":"","deeplink":""}},"normalNotePreloadData":{"desc":"不要总盯着文本模型，梳理一下世界模型的两种思路\nLLM在物理世界中受限，Yann LeCun提出JEPA架构，AI通过“心智模拟”理解现实。李飞飞的World Labs开发3D空间智能，AI将具备感知和操作能力。\n2026 年，开发者该往哪走？\n这是一场从“文本模型”到“物理 AI”的范式转移。\n• 对企业而言： 避开卷到极致的对话机器人，真正的蓝海在具身智能（Embodied AI）、工业孪生和机器人仿真。\n• 对开发者而言： 掌握 JEPA 风格的编码器和 3D 空间表征。LLM 将回归它作为“界面层”的本质，而基于空间智能的“世界模型”才是真正的核心。","imagesList":[{"width":1440,"url":"http:\u002F\u002Fsns-na-i6.xhscdn.com\u002F1040g00831v0gbkgg3q005o2gef4g8a5lvm10i18?imageView2\u002F2\u002Fw\u002F576\u002Fformat\u002Fwebp\u002Fq\u002F87%7CimageMogr2\u002Fstrip&redImage\u002Fframe\u002F0&origin=0","urlSizeLarge":"http:\u002F\u002Fsns-na-i6.xhscdn.com\u002F1040g00831v0gbkgg3q005o2gef4g8a5lvm10i18?imageView2\u002F2\u002Fw\u002F1080\u002Fformat\u002Fwebp&origin=0","height":2400}],"title":"LLM已经不性感了，越来越觉得LeCun 与李飞"}},"profile":{"userInfo":{"follows":"-","fans":"-","likeAndCollect":"-","nickname":"","images":"","bannerImage":"","desc":"","redId":"","id":"","tags":[],"tabs":[{"id":"note","name":"笔记","public":true,"visible":true}],"collectionList":[],"userAccountStatus":undefined,"userPageWidgetsInfo":{"normalWidgetList":[]}},"noteCollectionList":[],"noteData":[],"notePage":1,"categoryInfo":[],"sortType":[],"goodsCardList":[],"tab":"note","activeTab":"0","showBottomBar":true,"canShowExpand":false,"jumpBackLink":""},"UseAbExpStore":{}}</script><script>window.__SETUP_SERVER_STATE__={"LAUNCHER_SSR_STORE_PAGE_DATA":{"noteData":{"atUserList":[],"time":1776293536000,"lastUpdateTime":1776293536000,"title":"LLM已经不性感了，越来越觉得LeCun 与李飞","desc":"不要总盯着文本模型，梳理一下世界模型的两种思路\nLLM在物理世界中受限，Yann LeCun提出JEPA架构，AI通过“心智模拟”理解现实。李飞飞的World Labs开发3D空间智能，AI将具备感知和操作能力。\n2026 年，开发者该往哪走？\n这是一场从“文本模型”到“物理 AI”的范式转移。\n• 对企业而言： 避开卷到极致的对话机器人，真正的蓝海在具身智能（Embodied AI）、工业孪生和机器人仿真。\n• 对开发者而言： 掌握 JEPA 风格的编码器和 3D 空间表征。LLM 将回归它作为“界面层”的本质，而基于空间智能的“世界模型”才是真正的核心。","interactInfo":{"shareCount":"652","followed":false,"sticky":false,"relation":"none","niceCount":"","collected":false,"commentCount":"152","collectedCount":"2,099","